    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>In this brief report, we point to virus infection time-dependent transcript levels of polymorphic ASMTL genes in human nasal epithelial cells from seven cell origins. Our observations encourage focused top-down and hypothesis-driven studies in support of more efficient allelic genotyping to identify targets for early resilience prediction.</jats:p>",
